data.description: This modern home is move-in ready and loaded with recent updates. In 2023, a fully remodeled kitchen was added, complete with custom-built cabinets, state-of-the-art appliances, and an eye-catching backsplash. The property also boasts a new outbuilding constructed in 2023, ensuring ample space for your needs. A new breaker box was installed in the same year, ensuring safety and convenience. Inside the home, you'll discover generously sized bedrooms, a spacious hallway, and a dining room featuring a fireplace and abundant natural light. The living room offers a cozy and welcoming atmosphere with its large windows. Outside, the property sits on a substantial 0.80-acre lot with nearly level terrain, perfect for creating your dream playground. Additional storage space is available in the partial basement. The house is in impeccable condition, with a new roof added in 2022, and it's ready for immediate occupancy. Don't miss your chance to make this modern and updated home yours!
